## 💡 About ArcSave

ArcSave is a decentralized savings protocol built on **Arc Testnet** that helps users earn passive income on their crypto assets safely and efficiently.

It is designed to make DeFi savings simple, transparent, and beginner-friendly.

---

## ⚡ Features

- 🔄 Auto yield optimization (testnet simulation)
- 💸 Simple deposit & withdraw system
- 🔍 Transparent on-chain transactions
- 🧠 Beginner-friendly interface
- 🔐 Secure and trustless system

